<div id="gs-profile-signup" class="section">
  <h2>Sign Up</h2>
  <p>
    You must be a group member in order to post to a group or receive email
    when someone posts to a group.
    Anyone can sign up and become a member of a <strong>public</strong>
    group.
    Signing up is a five-step process:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-group">Select a Group</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-email">Enter an email address</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-password">Set a password</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-profile">Change your profile</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify your email
      address</a></li>
  </ol>
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-group" class="section">
    <h3>Select a Group</h3>
    <p>
      The first step in signing up is selecting the group that you want to
      join.
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Visit the group that you wish to join.
      </li>
      <li>
        Click <samp class="link">Sign up and join.</samp>
        You will be taken to
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-email">the
          <cite class="page">Enter Email</cite> page.</a>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p class="note">
      <strong class="label">Note:</strong>
      If the group is <strong>private</strong> then you will have to
      <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">request membership</a>
      rather than sign up.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-email" class="section">
    <h3>Enter Email</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Enter your email address into the
        <samp class="entry">Email Address</samp> entry.
      </li>
      <li>
        Click the <samp class="button">Sign up</samp> button.
        You will be taken to
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-password">the <cite class="page">Set
          Password</cite> page.</a>
        In addition, an email message will be sent to you, verifying that
        you control the address you entered.
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p class="note">
      <strong class="label">Note:</strong> It is important that the email
      address for the support group &#8213;
      <code class="email"
            tal:content="view/siteInfo/get_support_email">foo@example.com</code>
      &#8213; is added to your address book.
    </p>
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-email-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-password" class="section">
    <h3>Set Password</h3>
    <p>
      Your password will be used to protect your personal information.
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Enter a password in the
        <cite class="entry">Password</cite> entry.
      </li>
      <li>
        Click the <cite class="button">Set</cite> button.
        Your password will be sent, and you will be taken to
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-profile">the <cite class="page">Change
            Profile</cite> page</a>
        page.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-password-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-profile" class="section">
    <h3>Change Profile</h3>
    <p>
      Your profile says a little about you, so others can find out the
      names of the group members.
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Enter your name in the
        <samp class="entry">Name</samp> entry.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="label">(Optional)</strong>
        Select your <cite class="wordasword">timezone</cite>
        from the <samp class="list">Timezone</samp> list.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="label">(Optional)</strong>
        Write a little about yourself in the
        <samp class="textarea">Biography</samp> entry.
      </li>
      <li>
        Click the <samp class="button">Change</samp> button.
        Your profile will be change, and you will be taken to
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">the
          <cite class="page">Verify Email</cite> page.</a>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p class="note">
      <strong class="label">Note:</strong>
      Some sites may provide extra fields on the
      <cite class="page">Change Profile</cite> page.
    </p>
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-profile-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-verify" class="section">
    <h3>Verify Email</h3>
    <p>
      You must verify that you control your email address.
      To verify your email address carry out the following tasks.
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>Check your email <cite class="wordasword">inbox.</cite>
        It should contain a message asking you to verify the
        address.
        If it does not, go through the procedures in
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble">Trouble Shooting</a>
        below.</li>
      <li>Click the link in the email.
        You will be taken to the <cite class="page">Verify Email
          Address</cite> page.</li>
      <li>Wait while your address is verified. You will
        be shown a confirmation message once this is done.</li>
      <li>Close the <cite class="page">Verify Email Address</cite> page.</li>
      <li>Find the window showing the
        <cite class="page">Awaiting Verification</cite> page.
        The <samp class="button">Finish</samp> button on the page will
        be available.</li>
      <li>
        Click on the <samp class="button">Finish</samp> button to finish
        sign up.
        You will be taken to the group your selected in the initial step.
      </li>
    </ol>
    <div id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble" class="section">
      <h4>Trouble Shooting</h4>
      <p>
        If your email does not contain a message asking you to verify
        your address, carry out the following tasks.
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-junk">
          Check your email <samp class="folder">Junk</samp> (or
          <samp class="folder">Spam</samp>) folder to see if the message
          is there.
          If it is then you should go carry out steps 2&#8213;5 in the
          <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify Email</a> section
          above.</li><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-junk-->
        <li id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-correct">
          Check that your email address is correct.
          If the address is incorrect
          <ol>
            <li>Enter a new address in the
              <samp class="entry">Email Address</samp> entry.</li>
            <li>Click the
              <samp class="entry">Send</samp> button.
              A new verification email will be sent to you.</li>
            <li>Carry out the steps in the
              <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify Email</a> section
              above.</li>
          </ol>
        </li><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-correct-->
      </ol>
    </div><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-->
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-->
</div><!--gs-profile-signup-->
